6f6200f6-1d24-4075-a155-1b3cc8dcb214.title: Note
6f6200f6-1d24-4075-a155-1b3cc8dcb214.text: Unknown if dialogue changes at all

5f969b2c-c526-4ce4-9249-6962178a9d11.title: Ponts the Bridgemaster
5f969b2c-c526-4ce4-9249-6962178a9d11.text:
Stop! Whoever crosses this bridge must answer me
these questions three.

73f30ce6-bc1a-46c1-ba45-fc1a53b75bdf.title: <player>
73f30ce6-bc1a-46c1-ba45-fc1a53b75bdf.text: Ask me the questions, bridgemaster. I am not afraid.

f3d39fe8-a2aa-4fcb-9bb7-1283bdba7f6e.title: Ponts the Bridgemaster
f3d39fe8-a2aa-4fcb-9bb7-1283bdba7f6e.text:
Well, perhaps. You should speak to Alec the Guildmaster.
He sorts out that kind of thing. You'll find him up on a
small island north of the guild.

214da394-4006-4006-a362-464af8eec0cb.title: <player>
214da394-4006-4006-a362-464af8eec0cb.text: Oh, okay! I'll go do that. Bye.

be43e1f8-e323-4a6c-acd8-62249578947a.title: Ponts the Bridgemaster
be43e1f8-e323-4a6c-acd8-62249578947a.text: What... is the capital of Kandarin?

options.text: How can a single kingdom have multiple kings?

8530549a-ef71-4f3c-b133-82c94803c935.title: <player>
8530549a-ef71-4f3c-b133-82c94803c935.text: Oh, er... I thought I was going to die.

0d88ef62-145b-462d-b8db-fdc8c2a68d4d.title: <player>
0d88ef62-145b-462d-b8db-fdc8c2a68d4d.text: I don't know. So can I go by?

db5cbcaf-835d-48e8-9ade-5adbc7d29a3a.title: Ponts the Bridgemaster
db5cbcaf-835d-48e8-9ade-5adbc7d29a3a.text:
There's always someone who wants to be difficult. Off
with you!

2eb84217-41a8-46c2-9a51-cf17779e95a9.title: <player>
2eb84217-41a8-46c2-9a51-cf17779e95a9.text: How can a single kingdom have multiple kings?

928687fa-824f-438b-beaa-dab5ef87286c.title: Ponts the Bridgemaster
928687fa-824f-438b-beaa-dab5ef87286c.text: What... is the air-speed velocity of an unladen chompy?

options.text: What do you mean? A Feldip chompy or one from Karamja?

3031753e-dc4c-40ef-b53b-a518f6ea5586.title: <player>
3031753e-dc4c-40ef-b53b-a518f6ea5586.text:
What do you mean? A Feldip chompy or one from
Karamja?

fbdbfddd-d8fd-4734-910c-78ebf5d45a3e.title: Ponts the Bridgemaster
fbdbfddd-d8fd-4734-910c-78ebf5d45a3e.text: Huh? I... I don't know that. ARGHHH!

626fc1e1-5664-43c0-9c52-001d1e08bd2c.title: Ponts the Bridgemaster
626fc1e1-5664-43c0-9c52-001d1e08bd2c.text:
Internal self-doubt and the crippling feeling of everyone
hating me.

67b34fe2-e336-4b27-ba37-853c875bedf8.title: <player>
67b34fe2-e336-4b27-ba37-853c875bedf8.text: Okay then... perhaps I should go past.

a22944a2-34e4-448d-8c11-094e896956c8.title: Ponts the Bridgemaster
a22944a2-34e4-448d-8c11-094e896956c8.text:
I'm sure I've seen them fly before, but it could've been
falling gracefully.

8cbd27cb-030b-4d9f-a421-9d53073efd4f.title: <player>
8cbd27cb-030b-4d9f-a421-9d53073efd4f.text: 11 meters per second, or 24 miles an hour.
